ml` crate is a thin wrapper whose `[lib] path` points to `../../library/proc_macro/src/lib.rs`. The bridge modules include: `mod.rs` (core types/RPC protocol, BridgeConfig), `client.rs` (client-side Bridge TLS state), `server.rs` (ExecutionStrategy, SameThread), `rpc.rs`, `handle.rs`, `buffer.rs`, `arena.rs`, `symbol.rs`, `fxhash.rs`, `closure.rs`, `selfless_reify.rs`."
}

