bridge_and_client`). The `compiler/rustc_proc_macro/Cargo.toml` crate provides a wrapper that points its `[lib] path` to `../../library/proc_macro/src/lib.rs`, making the same proc_macro library available to the compiler. The bridge modules include: `mod.rs` (core types/RPC protocol), `client.rs` (client-side Bridge TLS), `server.rs` (ExecutionStrategy, SameThread), `rpc.rs`, `handle.rs`, `buffer.rs`, `arena.rs`, `symbol.rs`, `fxhash.rs`, `closure.rs`, `selfless_reify.rs`."
}

